/Northern_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that it would be very helpful if the powers that be would give more money to sport because we get so much joy out of success, and we have got the stars.\\\"\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the powers\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"more money\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"so much joy\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the stars\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lady Mary's trust has supported 27Olympiansfrom Northern Ireland, including Scott.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_I_of_England\", \"score\": 0.9883712076919118, \"rank\": 0.007626573294912224, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_I_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_I_of_England\"}, {\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997264191102264, \"rank\": 0.00027365255832267535, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.9999527469975045, \"rank\": 3.0362029511103398e-05, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We get so much pleasure out of seeing so many of them do well, not only at the Olympic level, but world, European and Commonwealth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much pleasure\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic level\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that winning an Olympic gold changes an athlete's life forever.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic gold\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's life\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wonder, if I had been second, where I would be now.\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It changes your life forever.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you have won, you are always an Olympic champion,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted 